  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sesame oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add the tofu and cook until golden brown, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the shredded carrots and zucchini and cook until tender, about 4-5 minutes.",
    "Add the bean sprouts and cook until heated through, about 1-2 minutes.",
    "Add the gochujang and soy sauce and stir to combine.",
    "Add the khus khus, crushed candy, and green onions and stir to combine.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Transfer the Jjigae to a serving platter and serve immediately."
